-- Serenity: minimal UI shell. The old feature-rich hub has been set aside (full copy
-- kept in Main_Legacy_Full.lua) in favor of a clean rebuild -- blank slate with window
-- chrome (title, minimize, drag), a Home tab, and a Player tab with just Speed so far.
